<ab facs="#facs_212_r2l28">künglich durchlewhtıkeit cʒü allen cʒeiten vvılleklıch vnd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r2l29"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ̃ . <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan> Nereÿ et Achılej . ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
